# VPS Contabo host key — PINNED for CD (no TOFU / no ssh-keyscan at runtime).
#
# This file starts empty on purpose: CD fails loudly until you paste the real key,
# so a deploy can never trust an unverified host.
#
# To populate it, from a machine that ALREADY trusts the VPS (e.g. your laptop that
# has deployed before), run:
#
#     ssh-keyscan -t ed25519 45.90.123.190
#
# Verify the fingerprint matches what your SSH client shows, then paste the output
# line (NOT starting with '#') below this comment block and commit it.
